text: Gong Maoxin and Zhang Ze were the defending champions but lost in the semifinals to Aliaksandr Bury and Peng Hsien-yin. Denys Molchanov and Igor Zelenay won the title after defeating Bury and Peng 7–5, 7–6(7–4) in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Zhuhai Open - Men's Doubles 2018 Men's Doubles
